                    <h1>Getting Started with DropLaa</h1>
                    
                    <p>Welcome to DropLaa! This documentation will help you get started with our secure file sharing platform and make the most of all available features.</p>
                    
                    <h2>What is DropLaa?</h2>
                    <p>DropLaa is a secure, fast, and easy-to-use file sharing platform that allows you to send large files to anyone, anywhere. With bank-level encryption and no file size limits on premium plans, DropLaa is perfect for both personal and business use.</p>
                    
                    <h2>Quick Start Guide</h2>
                    <p>Follow these simple steps to share your first file:</p>
                    
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Visit the Upload Page:</strong> Navigate to the main upload area on our homepage</li>
                        <li><strong>Select Your Files:</strong> Drag and drop files or click to browse your device</li>
                        <li><strong>Upload:</strong> Click the upload button to start transferring your files</li>
                        <li><strong>Share:</strong> Copy the generated link and share it with your recipients</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <div class="info-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> No account registration is required for basic file sharing. Simply upload and share!
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2>File Upload Limits</h2>
                    <p>Different plans have different file size and storage limits:</p>
                    
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Free Plan:</strong> Up to 2GB per file, 5 files per upload</li>
                        <li><strong>Pro Plan:</strong> Up to 10GB per file, unlimited files per upload</li>
                        <li><strong>Business Plan:</strong> Up to 100GB per file, unlimited uploads</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h2>Security Features</h2>
                    <p>DropLaa implements multiple layers of security to protect your files:</p>
                    
                    <h3>End-to-End Encryption</h3>
                    <p>All files are encrypted using AES-256 encryption during transfer and storage. This ensures that only you and your intended recipients can access the files.</p>
                    
